&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Fundraise Up, we are reimagining the fundraising platform to create the fastest and most convenient way to donate to non-profit foundations. Our innovation is aimed at enhancing loading speeds, boosting conversion rates, offering diverse payment methods, and more. Each month, individuals worldwide donate tens of millions of dollars through our platform. We are the go-to fundraising solution for some of the world&#39;s leading non-profit organizations. UNICEF, The Obama Foundation, the Alzheimer&#39;s Association, and many others leverage our platform for their online fundraising needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;874&quot; data-end=&quot;1058&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;874&quot; data-end=&quot;1058&quot;&gt;We’re looking for a high-performing Account Executive to join our growing UK team. This is a true new business role focused on building and converting a strong pipeline across&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;SMB and Mid-Market (MM) segments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1060&quot; data-end=&quot;1310&quot;&gt;You’ll be someone who thrives in a fast-paced, high-growth environment, enjoys consultative selling, and is confident engaging senior stakeholders (including C-suite). You’re commercially driven, naturally curious, and motivated by exceeding targets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;1iaq00q&quot; data-start=&quot;1406&quot; data-end=&quot;1434&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1410&quot; data-end=&quot;1434&quot;&gt;What You’ll Be Doing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1436&quot; data-end=&quot;2062&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;xwc3z0&quot; data-start=&quot;1436&quot; data-end=&quot;1522&quot;&gt;Drive new business by educating prospective customers on the value of Fundraise Up.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;y1oowz&quot; data-start=&quot;1523&quot; data-end=&quot;1603&quot;&gt;Build, qualify, and manage a high-value pipeline of enterprise opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;hpqe0k&quot; data-start=&quot;1604&quot; data-end=&quot;1693&quot;&gt;Own the full sales cycle, including participation in formal procurement/RFP processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;9ubblr&quot; data-start=&quot;1694&quot; data-end=&quot;1778&quot;&gt;Partner with Marketing and Partnerships to identify and develop new lead sources.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1t1chqp&quot; data-start=&quot;1779&quot; data-end=&quot;1846&quot;&gt;Deliver compelling virtual and in-person product demonstrations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;32noug&quot; data-start=&quot;1847&quot; data-end=&quot;1920&quot;&gt;Engage and influence senior stakeholders across complex organisations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1e51mb3&quot; data-start=&quot;1921&quot; data-end=&quot;1998&quot;&gt;Collaborate with BDRs to refine outbound strategy and pipeline generation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;8s8unv&quot; data-start=&quot;1999&quot; data-end=&quot;2062&quot;&gt;Consistently exceed revenue targets and performance metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;1hr9x9o&quot; data-start=&quot;2069&quot; data-end=&quot;2099&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2073&quot; data-end=&quot;2099&quot;&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;2101&quot; data-end=&quot;2644&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;3w2c8v&quot; data-start=&quot;2101&quot; data-end=&quot;2157&quot;&gt;2+ years’ experience in B2B or enterprise SaaS sales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;mm4gal&quot; data-start=&quot;2158&quot; data-end=&quot;2223&quot;&gt;Experience carrying a quota of £750,000+ ARR&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;g5nji2&quot; data-start=&quot;2224&quot; data-end=&quot;2275&quot;&gt;Proven track record of closing six-figure deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1o0

&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;About Fundraise Up&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;We’re Fundraise Up - a global fundraising platform built to make donating to nonprofits fast, seamless, and accessible to all. Every month, our technology powers tens of millions of dollars in donations across the globe. We focus on innovation that directly impacts results: faster load times, higher conversion rates, global payment support, and accessibility-first design.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Our platform is trusted by many of the world’s leading nonprofits, including UNICEF, the Alzheimer’s Association, and a wide range of global NGOs. With a 4.9/5 rating across top software review platforms, we’re recognized not just for our impact - but for the quality of the product we deliver.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;notion-enable-hover&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot; data-token-index=&quot;0&quot;&gt;About The Role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an SMB Business Development Representative, you are a critical driver of our growth. While our Enterprise team focuses on a handful of massive organizations, you will manage a territory of &lt;strong&gt;2,000+ accounts&lt;/strong&gt;. This is a high-volume, high-activity role designed for someone who thrives on structure, repetition, and the challenge of finding the right entry point into a busy nonprofit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This isn’t just about making dials or sending emails; it’s about managing a massive funnel. You will be responsible for identifying the right moment to reach out - whether a nonprofit just hired a new director, launched a new program, or is engaging with our content. We are a startup, which means we need people who will experiment with us, find what works, and help us validate the playbook for this segment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;notion-enable-hover&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot; data-token-index=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hit Your Numbers:&lt;/strong&gt; Your target is &lt;strong&gt;15 meetings booked per month&lt;/strong&gt;, with a focus on quality. At least &lt;strong&gt;9 of those must be qualified&lt;/strong&gt; by an Account Executive to count toward your core goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the Meeting Attendance:&lt;/strong&gt; A booked meeting only matters if the prospect shows up. You are responsible for the pre-meeting follow-up, sending reminders and relevant information to ensure the prospect is prepared and excited to talk to us. You also re-engage and re-set missed meetings/demos.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Execute High-Volume Outreach:&lt;/strong&gt; You will manage a large territory using a mix of phone, email, and LinkedIn. You’ll need to balance several outreach campaigns at once and ensure 100+ dials among other touch points.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Respond to Intent:&lt;/strong&gt; You will be the primary point of contact for prospects who are already interacting with us - downloading our guides, visiting our site, or attending our webinars. Speed and relevance are key here - warming these accounts and territory is critical - ensure meaningful activity and ROE.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Personalize Strategically:&lt;/strong&gt; In a territory of 2,000+ accounts, you can&#39;t research every lead for an hour. You will learn to use &quot;scalable personalization&quot;; identifying key triggers like new hires or fundraising goals to make your outreach stand out.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Teammate People Want to Work With: &lt;/strong&gt;You bring a positive, optimistic attitude even when facing the adversity of h

