&lt;p data-start=&quot;851&quot; data-end=&quot;1101&quot;&gt;This role is well-suited to someone who combines a strong commercial instinct with a thoughtful, consultative approach. You’re comfortable opening doors, leading with insight, and guiding senior stakeholders through meaningful, high-impact decisions.&lt;/p&gt;
